                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>She elaborated that people discussing PPD more as "a neurobiological occurrence" clarifies that PPD is not viewed as "a sign of weakness."&nbsp;</p>
<p>"It's not something you did. It's not your fault," Marx said. "I think that will go a long way to trying to combat the disorder overall."</p>
